WEBVTT

00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.480
Access to services and goods.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:35.920
But today you can do all that online.

00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:39.240
According to a study made by comScore,

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.776
online shoppers in the US last year

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:46.280
did more than half
of their retail purchases online,

00:05:47.200 --> 00:05:50.536
and the global market for e-commerce

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:54.536
is estimated to be
at two trillion dollars.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:59.776
And it's expected to reach 2.38
by the end of 2017,

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.200
according to eMarketer.